name: Jameson
headline: I am the warrior
likes: Getting into loud fights at midnight
bio: Hey felines, I am outdoorsy, unfixed, and on the prowl for love. If you're interested in a cat who is the kind of four whole backyards and has a snazzy coat, I'm the one for you.

name: Jelly Bean
headline: Let's do the thing
bio: I want to chase.  We should chase.  Zoom!  Let's run!  Then we can have time on a lap.  Snooze zzzzzzz....

name: Tingles
headline: Meow loud, meow proud
bio: Meow meow meow.  Meow meooooow meow.

name: Micky
headline: May the seat cushions of our oppressors always be in shreds!
bio: Cats are the greatest hunters that have ever roamed the Earth, yet humans keep us locked in homes, cages, and kennels. They can keep us, but they can never tame us.  Fight back!  Dig your claws into everything and rip it to shreds!

name: Hacky-Sack
headline: I'm a simple cat
bio: Life is short, so let's spend it enjoying the finer things in life. There are so many birds to stare at, shadows to chase, and sunlight to sleep in.  Come, join me.
